✔ LocalDate.now()                           → Get the current date.
✔ LocalDateTime.now()                       → Get the current date & time.
✔ plusDays(n), minusDays(n)                 → Add/Subtract days.
✔ ChronoUnit.DAYS.between(date1, date2)     → Find date difference.
✔ Year.of(year).isLeap()                    → Check if a year is a leap year.
✔ DayOfWeek.from(date)                      → Get the day of the week from a date.
✔ ZoneId.systemDefault()                    → Get the current time zone.